      <para styleclass="Heading1"><text styleclass="Heading1" translate="true">Edit: Sweep-Display</text></para>
    </header>
    <para styleclass="Heading3_atocs_"><text styleclass="Heading3_atocs_" translate="true">Sweep-Display</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Use to evaluate exact motion-values at any </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">X-axis value </text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">as defined by the </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Cursor-Position</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> parameter. A vertical cursor shows at the </text><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">X-axis value</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true"> and </text><text styleclass="Parameter-Header" translate="true">Cursor-Position.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="VariableName" translate="true">BUG</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">: The Cursor does not sweep correctly when </text><text styleclass="Parameter" translate="true">Motion-Start ≠ 0</text><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">see </text><link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MT-BlendPoint-X-axis-Value" styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">Blend-Point Editor &gt; X-axis Values &gt; Motion-Start</link><text styleclass="Body Text" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">.</text></para>
    <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
    <para styleclass="Body Text"><table styleclass="Default" rowcount="3" colcount="2">
